Swap vertex modes in bipartite graphs.

Source: R/bipartite.R
bip_swap_modes.Rd

Swap vertex modes in bipartite graphs.

bip_swap_modes(x, ...)

# S3 method for igraph
bip_swap_modes(x)

# S3 method for network
bip_swap_modes(x, clarify_actors = TRUE)

Arguments

x

A bipartite igraph (igraph::graph) or network::network object.
clarify_actors

Whether to also run bip_clarify_actors() on network::network objects.

Examples
